<p><b> As Above, So Below </b></p>

<p> The Final Installment of Professor Bent's thoughts on S. Maria Novella </p>

<p><b>The Roof</b></p>

<p>Near the end of the project, Francesco invited me to climb the scaffolding on the outside of the Cappella Maggiore that covers the church exterior that faces the city train station. I jumped at the chance, not knowing exactly what was in store for me.</p>
